  "stem": "<p>One line in the <em>xy</em>-plane passes through the points <math><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfenced></math> and <math><mfenced><mrow><mn>8</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>. A second line passes through the points <math><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></math> and <math><mfenced><mrow><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>. What is the solution <math><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math> of the system formed by these two lines?</p>",
